# Template Tags Example

<% 
// You can execute any JavaScript here
const playerName = "Hero";
const score = Math.floor(Math.random() * 100);
const currentTime = new Date().toLocaleTimeString();
%>

**Welcome, <%= playerName %>!**

**Your current score:** <%= score %> points

**Current time:** <% print(currentTime); %>

Template tags in Snowman:
- `<% code %>` - Execute JavaScript
- `<%= value %>` - Output a value 
- `<%- html %>` - Output raw HTML

